{"tid":1216444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]  台灣中油油輪阿曼灣遭襲爆炸   7.5萬噸石油腦全毀","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:17:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"856fb2b8e91e63b1cb7b0ca2b613186fcc50f3a4","tid":1216444,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"中油油輪阿曼灣遭襲爆炸 7.5萬噸石油腦全毀<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2821338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821338&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=02fd43e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2821338&h=0a68831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2821338</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者黃佩君／台北報導〕美伊局勢升高影響區域情勢緊張，今傳出兩艘大型油輪在阿曼海域遭魚雷攻擊，其中有一艘Front Altair屬於中油租用，輪上載運運7.5萬噸石油腦全數遭毀，船員已棄船。伊朗媒體表示有油輪爆炸，國際油價聞訊飆升達4%。中油目前未有高層主管回應，僅表示目前正在釐清此訊息，對相關影響也在進行評估中。<br />\n<br />\n美伊局勢升高也影響區域情勢，5月初沙烏地阿拉伯兩艘油輪12日在荷姆茲海峽附近遇襲受創，全球最重要運油動脈遭阻。<br />\n<br />\n今又傳出停泊在阿曼灣的兩艘大型油輪遇襲爆炸，油輪Front Altair被目擊起火，另一艘巴拿馬籍油輪則為Kokuka Courageous，消息傳出後國際油價飆升4%。<br />\n<br />\n外電報導，巴基斯坦當地表示，油輪已向海上沿岸國家發出求救電話。而英國海上貿易運營部也警告，在阿曼灣發生了一起未明事件，敦促在當地航行要「極其謹慎」。<br />\n<br />\n對此事件，中油目前尚未有所反應，高層均表示尚在調查中、不清楚詳細情況，稍晚將會發布聲明。"},{"pid":"38b15b4b38b2e051ea9b8ac804956f4eead9b7af","tid":1216444,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee04d4d9cee808a6c1594cae732de7f5f8697812","tid":1216444,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"台灣佬唔聽侵侵話買伊朗油?<br />\n整返支MK48雪卡先啦。"},{"pid":"b46717b9bacfd20711ed0d104ff4c99468fd4973","tid":1216444,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"太好啦"},{"pid":"89f21d7c26b91358f913c305383f6fad7648ffa9","tid":1216444,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"魚雷"},{"pid":"533a2cdc6919dc7f22ba0aa576146ce3043fbc7b","tid":1216444,"uid":35648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"日本都話有一隻關佢地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5459faee7c0ce58ddd229afda6392100249637","tid":1216444,"uid":5822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"台灣呢2日咁多野講 唔洗問都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305bfc0ee78ef7ed880bd7741680addf2b070901","tid":1216444,"uid":6548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"支那扮其他國家玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一係收左支那錢玩"},{"pid":"55f2cc868d815490b1cd70b7434dbc8ec4d17772","tid":1216444,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"逼台灣重開核電??"},{"pid":"4c252772c97bee525f25e8c67cb5b59c1de53a00","tid":1216444,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee04d4d9cee808a6c1594cae732de7f5f8697812","tid":1216444,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"台灣佬唔聽侵侵話買伊朗油?<br />\n整返支MK48雪卡先啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:17:25.000Z","msg":"可能係滯台支人"}]}